articles.title: Awareness of the link between HPV and cancer according to cancer type and gender in the US from 2014-2020.
articles.summary: HPV awareness varies by cancer type and gender, with high cervical cancer knowledge declining and low awareness for other HPV-related cancers remaining stable from 2014-2020.

articles.title: Endobronchial ultrasound-guided mediastinal biopsies for the diagnosis of mediastinal diseases: A network meta-analysis.
articles.summary: A network meta-analysis shows endobronchial ultrasound-guided biopsies effectively diagnose mediastinal diseases, particularly in lung cancer staging.
